{
  "_comment": "Source of truth for which envs go in which webinstaller group. The sync_release.py script regenerates each manifest.json from this plus the offsets.json embedded in the release's webinstall zip. The `name` field must match what the running firmware advertises over Improv (ImprovSerial::send_device_info) so esp-web-tools recognises the upgrade as same-firmware and preserves NVS without prompting the user to erase. Version is supplied separately via the manifest's `version` field, not embedded in `name`.",
